ces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"省？珠海市澳門鎮咋"},{"pid":"037fcad90f5a0077ba03163e775da3618e22f5c4","tid":1603553,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"大三巴牌坊光雕綻彩 與眾齊賀國慶<br />\n<br />\n【澳門日報消息】為慶賀中華人民共和國成立七十周年，旅遊局今起至國慶日，一連三晚在大三巴牌坊特別呈獻以&ldquo;共慶七十華誕共享偉大榮光&rdquo;為主題的光雕表演，與居民和旅客一起歡度節慶。<br />\n<br />\n光雕表演今晚8時至10時進行，明後兩晚表演則安排在7時至10時上演，在該時段內每隔15分鐘將進行約5分鐘的光雕表演，光雕表演的故事內容分兩部分，分別是&ldquo;澳門居民同心同賀&rdquo;，以及&ldquo;歡欣吉祥！共慶七十華誕&rdquo;。今晚首場表演準時在8時開始，現場吸引大批居民和旅客駐足觀賞，場面熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=8960590_aomen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fh5.newaircloud.com%2Fnews_detail%3Fnewsid%3D8960590_aomen&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=cc51e1c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://h5.newaircloud.com/news_detail?newsid=8960590_aomen</a>"},{"pid":"17dc3beef1f889c0c0361693436f6f0e161eaee4","tid":1603553,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"93151e2f2aaa355ddedad491d7d28335d55bf73e","tid":1603553,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"为庆贺中华人民共和国成立70周年<br />\n<br />\n澳门大三巴牌坊的光雕表演<br />\n将从9月29日（今天）起一连三晚<br />\n隆重上演！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/344182845_383547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F344182845_383547&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=6de154d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/344182845_383547</a>"}]}